You can just used tagged enums and the inline else syntax, like this:<p><pre><code>  const Animal = union(enum) {
      cat: Cat,
      dog: Dog,

      pub fn make_noise(self: Animal) void {
          switch (self) {
              inline else =&gt; |impl| impl.make_noise(),
          }
      }
  };</code></pre>

